    Scope and Contents
Narrators discuss their association and experiences with Springfield poet Vachel Lindsay (1879-1931). Also discussed are Lindsay's parents, the family home in Springfield, his poetry and tours, his marriage, and tragic death. Nicholas Lindsay is the poet's son. English, Dr. Thomas H. (1895-1992), 1 tape, 45 mins., 9 pp. 
